<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Post Only - No Form</title>
    <script>
        
		// This is to test the API
		// Sending data in JSON format using POST method
        // This is working by opening "http://localhost/post_only.gohtml" in browser
		
        var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
        var url = "/todos";
        xhr.open("POST", url, true);
        var data = JSON.stringify({"description": "record posted by post_only.gohtml", "complete": true});
        xhr.send(data);
		
    </script>
</head>
<body>
<p>This is to test the API
<p>Sending data in JSON format using POST method
<p>This is working by opening <a href="http://localhost/post_only.gohtml">http://localhost/post_only.gohtml</a> in browser
</body>
</html>